nodes.text: Ken-Kiba's spice runner gang operated on the planet of Telerath and its second moon. Led by Ken-Kiba, the gang was considered by some to be more dangerous than its rival - Musori's slaver gang. In 19 BBY, a former Jedi, Dass Jennir, attacked the gang's operation on the moon. He freed all the slaves, consisting of Nosaurians and Chubbits, and killing all the gangsters who stood in his way.
